# Build artifacts
aicap-linux-amd64
aicap.exe

# Local editor/assistant context — kept out of the repo.
CLAUDE.md
.claude/

# --- Documentation split ------------------------------------------------
#
# documentation/ is PUBLIC: anything tracked there ships with the repo and
# is readable by every customer, auditor, and competitor who clones it.
#
# documentation/internal/ is PRIVATE and never tracked. Owner's notes live
# there — launch plans, funnel checklists, pricing working, outreach
# lists, internal status. The whole directory is ignored, so a new private
# note is private by default and nobody has to remember to add a rule for
# it. That default is the point: the previous per-file rules only worked
# if you thought to write one before committing.
#
# See documentation/README.md.
/documentation/internal/

# CI/test log artifacts dropped into the docs folder.
/documentation/*.log
